#

Spicy Black Bean and Quinoa Stuffed Peppers

$12.5
350 kcal

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianHigh-Protein

Tags:

DinnerVegetarian

Description

Colorful bell peppers stuffed with spicy black beans, corn, and topped with melted cheese for a delightful and protein-rich dinner.

Ingredients

  • Bell Peppers: 4 large
  • Black Beans: 1 can (15 oz), drained and rinsed
  • Corn: 1 cup, frozen or fresh
  • Cooked Quinoa: 1 cup
  • Onion: 1 medium, diced
  • Garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • Cumin: 1 tsp
  • Chili Powder: 1 tsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black Pepper: to taste
  • Cheddar Cheese: 1 cup, shredded (optional)
